OL,3,CDog rescue warns of increase of
OL,4,C'pandemic puppies' coming into their
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FA dog rescue charity in South Wales
OL,8,Fsays they're facing a surge in
OL,9,Frequests to take in unplanned or
OL,10,Funsold litters of puppies.
OL,12,FHope Rescue, in Llanharan, near
OL,13,FPontyclun, say the number of puppies
OL,14,Farriving with them has more than
OL,15,Ftrebled, compared to the same period
OL,16,Flast year, with the charity receiving
OL,17,Frequests to take in 85 puppies since
OL,18,Fthe start of the year.
