OL,3,CDog rescue warns of increase of
OL,4,C'pandemic puppies' coming into their
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F60 puppies came into Hope Rescue's
OL,8,Fcare between January and June 2024,
OL,9,Fcompared to 14 puppies during the same
OL,10,Fperiod in 2023.
OL,12,FA further 15 puppies came into Hope
OL,13,FRescue's care as part of their work
OL,14,Fsupporting local authorities and
OL,15,FAnimal Licensing Wales to tackle low
OL,16,Fwelfare and illegal breeding.
