OL,3,CDog rescue warns of increase of
OL,4,C'pandemic puppies' coming into their
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FThe litter of one female and three
OL,8,Fmales were abandoned without their
OL,9,Fmother.
OL,11,FAnother recent example they gave was
OL,12,FRobin the Pointer, who arrived at Hope
OL,13,FRescue after a call from her
OL,14,Fdistressed owner, just as Robin began
OL,15,Fgiving birth.
OL,17,FThe new-born litter of eight puppies
OL,18,Fand Robin were immediately brought
OL,19,Finto the rescue centre and given the
OL,20,Fcare they needed.
