OL,3,CDog rescue warns of increase of
OL,4,C'pandemic puppies' coming into their
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FThey say "the market for puppies has
OL,8,Freached saturation point and, with no
OL,9,Fpuppy buyers for the unplanned
OL,10,Flitters, desperate owners are
OL,11,Fcontacting Hope Rescue for help.
OL,13,F"However, like the rest of the sector,
OL,14,FHope Rescue is operating at capacity
OL,15,Fwith a rise in stray dogs and a
OL,16,Fslowing in the number of dogs being
OL,17,Fadopted. The puppy boom has truly gone
OL,18,Fbust."
